text MauvilleCity_BikeShop_Text_SpencerWouldBeNiceToHaveBikes {
	format ("SPENCER: Anyway…"
		"I was thinking. It would be nice if the three of us had bikes. "
		"We've traveled so far already, but we still have a long way to go. "
		"Having some bikes would help us cover distances that much quicker.\N"
		"Plus, we'd look super rad riding these around everywhere!\N"
		"I'm not sure we can afford them, though…")
}

